{"tid":1429987,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好文重推，壓止分化風氣","createTime":"2019-08-07T15:32:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T15:43:22.000Z","uid":195930,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3d2a9b6b764e32803f4a8556e127a1445009abce","tid":1429987,"uid":195930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:32:37.000Z","msg":"吸取教訓：日本社運失敗的歷史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1283959\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1283959</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不分化，不篤灰，不割𥱊</span><br />\n<br />\n尼場運動有一類人仲仆街過藍絲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1429592\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1429592</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我知道好多人都為左場運動付出好多時間，心力，甚至前途同家庭。<br />\n但係大家唔好因為計較大家付出幾多，而將自己既同路人講成比藍絲更仆街，請將槍口對準敵人。<br />\n場運動是因為大家各施各法先咁有效，唔洗入會儀式，唔洗報到。場仗係持久戰黎，唔好未打完場仗就開始攻擊自己人。<br />\n堅守三大原則<br />\n感謝各位既付出，我真係好自豪自己係香港人，一齊保護我地既家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56bb1e0accfd7c6aabbebcda39cb5e79b0fefc76","tid":1429987,"uid":195930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:35:19.000Z","msg":"唔好再內鬥"},{"pid":"cb77be1ab3c3c220aa69a3dd1e3887256e23347f","tid":1429987,"uid":195930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:36:29.000Z","msg":"見到成班人屌同路人好心痛"},{"pid":"be427dfa13852bc0a5460ccb10b82ade0a397251","tid":1429987,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:42:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YfpJdw6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYfpJdw6.jpg&h=6d3415f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cQSuTw6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcQSuTw6.jpg&h=d2115447&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/njOh2qs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnjOh2qs.jpg&h=27b59e15&s={SIZE}\" />"},